ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 254, Yukon
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER No. 254 in order to (1) declare the natural disaster to be of federal concern; and (2) authorize the provision of financial assistance to YUKON with respect to the spring flood and landslides that occurred from April 30 to July 20, 2022.
